--------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes on running both microservices together
--------------------------------------------------------------------
- Both projects default to server.port=8080, so starting the loan service
  while the account service is already running causes:
  "Web server failed to start. Port 8080 was already in use."
- Fix: add server.port=8081 to the loan microservice's application.properties.
- Both services can then run simultaneously: account on 8080, loan on 8081.
- In Eclipse, use the monitor icon in the Console view to switch between
  the two running console outputs.
